### Get all BuyMe requests
GET http://localhost:3000/api/buyme

### Get a single BuyMe request (replace :id with real request ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/buyme/:id

### Create a new BuyMe request
POST http://localhost:3000/api/buyme
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "PUT_A_REAL_USER_ID_HERE",
  "productName": "Nike Air Max",
  "productLink": "https://example.com/nike-air-max",
  "notes": "Size 42, Black"
}

### Update a BuyMe request (replace :id with real request ID)
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/buyme/:id
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "approved",
  "notes": "Admin approved this request"
}

### Delete a BuyMe request (replace :id with real request ID)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/buyme/:id
